title: [Liette's Outfitting]
[Liette's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath an etched seaglass ceiling, a faded treasure map hangs on one of the blue-speckled sea glass walls.  Some stained driftwood shelves and a Vornavian silk-covered table sit in opposite corners while some puffed raw silk pillows rests on a swirled sea glass floor.
